title: Mahomes Alone
description:
Mina Kimes and Domonique Foxworth recap Monday Night Football between the Chiefs & Raiders. What do they think about the controversial roughing the passer call? Plus, they give their Winners & Woofs for Week 5! Brian Daboll is making his case for Coach of the Year as the Giants are now 4-1 to start the season after beating the Packers in London. Plus, John Harbaugh makes all the right calls in Week 5 to earn himself a spot on the winner’s list. And on the other side, they react to Matt Rhule’s firing while still being owed $40 million.
